
Q Computer

Instruction Set

BASIC INSTRUCTIONS

OPD	OPH	INSTRUCTION		ARGUMENTS
0	0	NONE
1	1	LOAD 			REG VALUE
2	2	LOAD_RAM 		REG ADDR
3	3	STORE			VALUE ADDR
4	4	STORE_REG		REG ADDR
 
8	8	ADD				REG REG
9	9	SUB				REG REG
10	A	MUL				REG REG
11	B	DIV				REG REG

16	10	CMP				REG REG
17	11	JMP				ADDR
18	12	JE				ADDR
19	13	JNE				ADDR
20	14	JG				ADDR
21	15	JGE				ADDR
22	16	JL				ADDR
23	17	JLE 			ADDR

MEMORY ADDRESSES
Important Memory Addresses are listed below.
They can be useful for program development.

All of the following memory addresses are read-only.
Nothing will happen if you write to them.

512		0x200	HARDWARE
513		0x201 	Current Key
513		0x202	Current Mouse Button
514		0x203	Current Mouse X
515		0x204	Current Mouse Y

528		0x210	Monitor Size X
529		0x211	Monitor Size Y



